<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想试着说一次，<delay20 />
“这些我全包了”之类的话！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在商店<delay8 />一见钟情的商品，<delay20 />
